name: Aditi Patel
summary: Aditi Patel is a 30-year-old straight woman, standing 5'4" tall, who currently lives in Los Angeles, California. She was born in San Jose, California, and is of South Asian ethnicity. She identifies with the pronouns She/Her/Hers and she describes herself as a Liberal Hindu. Aditi is highly educated, having graduated from the University of California - Berkeley, and works in the Technology industry as a Software Engineer. Aditi values education, hard work, kindness, and inclusivity. Her hobbies include hiking, coding, painting, and cooking. She occasionally drinks, does not smoke, use marijuana, or drugs, and she maintains an active lifestyle. Aditi does not have any children but is looking forward to having some one day. She speaks English, Hindi, and Spanish. She is looking for a straight man who is between 28 and 35 years old, is at least 5'5" tall, does not have children yet but wants them in the future, maintains an active lifestyle and shares her views on drinking, smoking, and substance use. She owns a pet cat and her zodiac sign is Leo.
